WEBVTT

00:00:04.516 --> 00:00:13.863 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In my reading and my study,
There are treasures that I find

00:00:13.863 --> 00:00:23.306 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When I’m searching, digging deeper,
When I take a little time.

00:00:23.306 --> 00:00:29.412 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In my imagination, I am in the scene.

00:00:29.412 --> 00:00:35.552 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It helps me understand 
just what the Bible means.

00:00:35.552 --> 00:00:44.649 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Imagination and meditation—​
​These are the things that help me see.

00:00:44.649 --> 00:00:54.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They give the insight to help me do right
And be the person I should be—​

00:00:54.104 --> 00:00:57.407 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
​The person I should be.

00:00:59.442 --> 00:01:08.418 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I can ponder on the people—​
​Some were faithful; some were not.

00:01:08.418 --> 00:01:18.361 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Their example gives me insight
To God’s feelings and his thought.

00:01:18.361 --> 00:01:24.332 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sometimes my meditation makes me realize

00:01:24.332 --> 00:01:30.306 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How I can be 
more pleasing in Jehovah’s eyes.

00:01:30.306 --> 00:01:39.482 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Imagination and meditation—​
​These are the things that help us see.

00:01:39.482 --> 00:01:48.216 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They give the insight to help us do right
And be the persons we should be—​

00:01:48.216 --> 00:01:53.797 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
​The persons we should be.

00:01:53.797 --> 00:01:58.201 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Imagination and meditation,

00:01:58.201 --> 00:02:02.405 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Imagination and meditation,

00:02:02.405 --> 00:02:08.611 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Imagination and meditation.

